From: Peter Gonda <pgonda@google.com>
Date: Wed, 27 Jan 2021 08:15:24 -0800
Subject: [PATCH] Fix unsynchronized access to sev members through
 svm_register_enc_region
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.10.15
Git-commit: 19a23da53932bc8011220bd8c410cb76012de004

commit 19a23da53932bc8011220bd8c410cb76012de004 upstream.

Grab kvm->lock before pinning memory when registering an encrypted
region; sev_pin_memory() relies on kvm->lock being held to ensure
correctness when checking and updating the number of pinned pages.

Add a lockdep assertion to help prevent future regressions.

